enchantment.netherdepthsupgrade.hell_str: As you glide through the molten rock, you feel a surge of speed and power coursing through your veins, allowing you to swim through lava with ease and grace.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_blazefish: Feast on a savory bowl of blazefish stew, made with juicy blazefish slices, creamy potatoes, rich eggs, and plump tomatoes, and watch your damage output soar with every fiery spoonful.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_glowdine_: Made with succulent slices of glowdine, creamy potatoes, rich eggs, and juicy tomatoes, you can feel your movement speed increase with every satisfying spoonful.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_lava_puff: Experience the fiery flavors of lava pufferfish stew, featuring tender slices of the exotic fish, creamy potatoes, rich eggs, and juicy tomatoes, all brought together in a savory broth that grants the gift of lava vision.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_magmacube: Filled with savory slices of fish and hearty vegetables, guaranteed to give you fire resistance and a warm glow from within.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_obsidianf: Brimming with tender slices of Obsidianfish, creamy potatoes, protein-packed eggs, and juicy tomatoes, all fortified with the empowering effects of Damage Resistance.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_searing_c: Experience the heat of the lava with a bowl of searing cod stew, brimming with succulent slices of searing cod, creamy potatoes, rich eggs, and ripe tomatoes. Each steaming spoonful will invigorate you with increased movement speed.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.baked_soulsucke: Crafted with succulent slices of Soulsucker, hearty potatoes, protein-packed eggs, and ripe tomatoes, all imbued with the magical essence of Absorption and Dig speed.
Experience the fiery flavor of blazefish in every bite a blazefish roll, made with succulent blazefish slices and perfectly cooked rice.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.blazefish_slice: Sizzling and steaming as they hit the cutting board, their fiery essence infusing the air with the smell of molten rock and burning magic.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.cooked_glowdine: Tender and juicy, the cooked glowdine slice is kissed by flames in the furnace, infusing it with a subtle, smoky essence that pairs perfectly with its naturally sweet, buttery flavor.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.cooked_lava_puf: The lava pufferfish slice, expertly cooked in the furnace to remove any toxins, reveals a succulent, tender flesh that is infused with a fiery, volcanic essence and a hint of sweetness.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.cooked_magmacub: Sizzling on the hot stones of the furnace, the magma cube fish slice exudes a tantalizing aroma that tempts the taste buds with its smoky, fiery flavors.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.cooked_obsidian: Glistening in the light, the heat of the furnace enhancing the shiny, black sheen of the obsidian skin as it adds a unique, smoky flavor to the tender fish meat.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.cooked_soulsuck: A slice exuding a rich, smoky aroma as it is served, the heat of the furnace bringing out the full flavor of the soulsucker's succulent flesh.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.glowdine_roll.f: Experience the otherworldly essence of the Nether with every bite of this glowdine roll, filled with delicate slices of the elusive, luminescent fish and wrapped in succulent sushi rice.
A soft and radiant glow can be seen permeating, the shimmering particles released from the fish's skin adding an otherworldly touch to the dish.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_blazefi: Indulge in the fiery flavors of the grilled blazefish, bursting with the heat of the Nether and enhanced with sweet berries, savory cabbage, and caramelized onions for a damage boost that will have you feeling unstoppable.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_glowdin: Savory and succulent, this grilled glowdine is bursting with the flavors of sweet berries, crunchy cabbage, and caramelized onions. One bite will leave you feeling light on your feet, thanks to its movement-enhancing properties.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_lava_pu: Indulge in the fiery flavor of grilled lava pufferfish, infused with sweet berries, crunchy cabbage, and savory onions, and gain the power of lava vision with every bite.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_magmacu: Feast on the sizzling, spicy goodness of grilled magma cube fish, bursting with the sweetness of berries and the crunch of cabbage and onions. As you savor each bite, you'll feel the heat of fire resistance burning within you.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_obsidia: Indulge in the smoky, succulent flavor of grilled obsidianfish, infused with the sweet tang of berries and the crunch of cabbage and onions. One bite and you'll feel the added bonus of damage resistance coursing through your veins.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_searing: Experience the savory, flame-kissed flavor of grilled searing cod, enhanced with the sweetness of berries and the crunch of cabbage and onions. As you enjoy this delicious dish, you'll feel your movement speed increase with each bite.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.grilled_soulsuc: Indulge in the savory, succulent flavors of the grilled soulsucker, bursting with the sweetness of berries and the crunch of cabbage and onions. Its heavenly taste is only surpassed by the positive effects it imparts, including a boost to your digging prowess and absorption capabilities.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.lava_pufferfish: Experience the spicy and fiery taste of lava pufferfish in a lava pufferfish roll, filled with thin slices of the exotic fish and perfectly cooked rice.
Sizzling on the cutting board, their fiery red skin a warning of the potentially toxic spines hidden within. Only the most skilled chefs dare to handle these dangerous, yet delicious fish.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.magmacubefish_r: Sizzling with the heat of a thousand volcanoes, this magma cube fish roll brings the fiery flavor of the Nether to your taste buds with every bite.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.magmacubefish_s: A steamy heat can be seen as they were expertly sliced on the cutting board, the vibrant red and orange hues of the magma cube fish's skin a testament to its fiery home
item.netherdepthsupgrade.nether_rice_rol: The nether rice roll medley is a true feast for the senses. Featuring a combination of warped kelp roll, magma cube fish roll, soulsucker roll, searing cod roll, lava pufferfish roll and glowdine roll, this block is sure to satisfy even the most adventurous palate.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.obsidianfish_ro: Experience the bold and unique flavor of obsidianfish in an obsidianfish roll, filled with thin slices of the rare fish and expertly cooked rice.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.obsidianfish_sl: Sizzling can be heard as they hit the hot pan, the black sheen of the obsidian skin gleaming in the light, a testament to the creature's survival in the molten depths of the lava.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.searing_cod_rol: Savor the bold and flavorful taste of searing cod in every bite of a searing cod roll, made with thin slices of the savory fish and perfectly cooked rice.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.searing_cod_sli: A sight to behold, the shimmering, searing flesh releasing waves of heat and energy as they hit the cutting board, almost as if they are alive and writhing in pain.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.soulsucker_roll: Indulge in the mysterious and addictive taste of soulsucker in a delectable soulsucker roll, made with thinly sliced soulsucker and perfectly cooked rice.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.soulsucker_slic: A dark and unsettling sight, their ethereal, shimmering flesh seeming to pulsate and writhe as they are cut on the cutting board, as if they are still alive and hungry for more souls.
item.netherdepthsupgrade.warped_kelp_rol: Indulge in the savory and slightly bizarre flavors of the signature warped kelp roll, made with tender strands of kelp, fluffy cooked rice, and crunchy carrots, all wrapped up in a perfectly crispy warped kelp wrapper.

Sliced from the popular warped kelp roll, this bite-sized piece packs a punch of flavor, with a hint of the bizarre and unexpected. Enjoy the combination of creamy rice, and crisp carrots, all wrapped up in a delicate warped kelp wrapper.
